text: Sybaguasu cornutum is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Galileo and Martins in 2005. It is known from Brazil.BioLib.cz - Sybaguasu cornutum. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2005
